{"type": "article", "id": 21291, "title": "樱花玻璃杯", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-26T08:23:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702133914NeMod2Zk7PlmtcgU.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t日本设计师坪井浩尚将樱花元素融入在玻璃杯的设计里，杯子的底部设计了五角樱花的图案。利用玻璃杯内外温差产生的冷凝效果，可以让杯子底部印出一个樱花的水渍。即便不去擦拭，水渍也会慢慢干掉，就像转瞬即逝的樱花。杯子是放在木盒里，配有透明和淡粉红两种颜色，很适合送礼。一套售价 4,860 日元起，这<a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/SAKURASAKU-glass-%E7%B4%85%E7%99%BD%E3%82%BB%E3%83%83%E3%83%88-%E3%82%BF%E3%83%B3%E3%83%96%E3%83%A9%E3%83%BC-%E3%81%95%E3%81%8F%E3%82%89%E3%81%95%E3%81%8F/dp/B00CR6Y6IC/ref=pd_bxgy_79_img_2/377-9065646-8991526?ie=UTF8&amp;refRID=01HX642QHVQBMXVYPQD3\" target=\"_blank\">里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150851i1qBPLhbEkVDuryK.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"406\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.634375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150851cvTx9J8P3Mrbmnap.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"406\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.634375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150851tGOARKENVsmeUyMw.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"406\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.634375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150852LDWQRug9ramfOxeh.jpg\" width=\"580\" height=\"446\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76896552\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}